---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="AI-Native GTM Transformation for B2B Executives | Treetop Growth Strategy"
  description="Your peers are rebuilding their revenue teams around AI and reporting results to their boards. Treetop designs the AI-native GTM architecture and gives you the roadmap to lead it internally."
>

<style>
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  .anim { animation: fadeUp 0.65s ease forwards; opacity: 0; }
  .d1{animation-delay:0.05s} .d2{animation-delay:0.18s} .d3{animation-delay:0.32s}
  .d4{animation-delay:0.46s} .d5{animation-delay:0.6s}

  .nav-link { font-size:0.82rem; font-weight:400; color:rgba(240,255,240,0.5); text-decoration:none; transition:color 0.2s; }
  .nav-link:hover { color:#F0FFF0; }

  .badge { display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:8px; font-size:0.72rem; font-weight:500; color:#00C853; letter-spacing:0.06em; }
  .badge-dot { width:7px; height:7px; border-radius:50%; background:#00C853; flex-shrink:0; }

  .btn-p { display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:6px; background:#00C853; color:#050D05; padding:0.875rem 1.75rem; font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif; font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:600; text-decoration:none; border:none; cursor:pointer; transition:opacity 0.2s,transform 0.15s; white-space:nowrap; }
  .btn-p:hover { opacity:0.88; transform:translateY(-1px); }

  .btn-g { display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:6px; background:transparent; color:#F0FFF0; padding:0.875rem 1.75rem; font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif; font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:600; text-decoration:none; border:1px solid #1A3A1A; transition:border-color 0.2s,background 0.2s; }
  .btn-g:hover { border-color:rgba(0,200,83,0.4); background:rgba(0,200,83,0.05); }

  .lbl { font-size:0.68rem; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:0.14em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#00C853; margin-bottom:1.25rem; display:block; }

  .card-dark { background:#050D05; border:1px solid #1A3A1A; padding:2rem; flex:1; min-width:0; transition:border-color 0.2s; }
  .card-dark:hover { border-color:rgba(0,200,83,0.35); }

  .card-mid { background:#0A1A0A; border:1px solid #1A3A1A; padding:2rem; flex:1; min-width:0; transition:border-color 0.2s,background 0.2s; }
  .card-mid:hover { border-color:rgba(0,200,83,0.35); background:#0f200f; }

  .step-row { display:flex; gap:1.5rem; align-items:flex-start; padding:2rem 0; border-bottom:1px solid #1A3A1A; }
  .step-row:last-child { border-bottom:none; }
  .step-bar { width:3px; min-height:60px; background:rgba(0,200,83,0.4); flex-shrink:0; align-self:stretch; }

  .rule { width:100%; height:1px; background:#1A3A1A; }

  .who-card { background:#050D05; border:1px solid #1A3A1A; padding:2rem; flex:1; min-width:240px; transition:border-color 0.2s; }
  .who-card:hover { border-color:rgba(0,200,83,0.35); }

  .quiz-box { border:1px solid rgba(0,200,83,0.25); background:#0A1A0A; padding:2.5rem; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:1rem; align-items:flex-start; }

  @media(max-width:768px){
    .mob-col { flex-direction:column !important; }
    .hide-mob { display:none !important; }
  }
</style>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav style="position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;z-index:50;background:rgba(5,13,5,0.95);backdrop-filter:blur(12px);border-bottom:1px solid #1A3A1A;">
  <div style="max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 2.5rem;height:64px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;">
    <a href="/" style="font-family:'Instrument Serif',serif;font-size:1.3rem;font-style:italic;color:#F0FFF0;text-decoration:none;">Treetop</a>
    <div class="hide-mob" style="display:flex;gap:2.5rem;align-items:center;">
      <a href="#process" class="nav-link">How It Works</a>
      <a href="#who" class="nav-link">Who It's For</a>
      <a href="#about" class="nav-link">About</a>
    </div>
    <a href="#contact" class="btn-p" style="padding:0.6rem 1.25rem;font-size:0.78rem;">Start the Conversation</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section style="min-height:100vh;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;padding:7rem 2.5rem 5rem;background:#050D05;">
  <div style="max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;width:100%;">
    <div class="badge anim d1" style="margin-bottom:2rem;"><span class="badge-dot"></span>AI-Native GTM Transformation</div>
    <h1 class="anim d2" style="font-family:'Instrument Serif',serif;font-size:clamp(2.8rem,6vw,5rem);font-weight:400;line-height:1.08;color:#F0FFF0;max-width:860px;margin-bottom:1.75rem;letter-spacing:-0.01em;">
      Lead Your Organization's<br/><span style="font-style:italic;color:#00C853;">AI Revenue</span><br/>Transformation.
    </h1>
    <p class="anim d3" style="font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:300;color:#8FAF8F;max-width:580px;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:2.5rem;">
      Your peers are rebuilding their revenue teams around AI — and reporting the results to their boards. Treetop designs the architecture and gives you the roadmap to lead it internally.
    </p>
    <div class="anim d4 mob-col" style="display:flex;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:2rem;">
      <a href="#contact" class="btn-p">Start the Conversation</a>
      <a href="/quiz" class="btn-g">Take the Gap Assessment →</a>
    </div>
    <p class="anim d5" style="font-size:0.75rem;color:rgba(240,255,240,0.25);letter-spacing:0.04em;">No pitch deck. No intake form. 30 minutes.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- THE SITUATION -->
<div class="rule"></div>
<section style="padding:5rem 2.5rem;background:#0A1A0A;">
  <div style="max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;">
    <span class="lbl">The Situation</span>
    <div class="mob-col" style="display:flex;gap:4rem;align-items:flex-start;">
      <div style="flex:1;min-width:260px;">
        <h2 style="font-family:'Instrument Serif',serif;font-size:clamp(1.8rem,3.5vw,2.6rem);font-weight:400;color:#F0FFF0;line-height:1.2;margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
          Most companies are buying AI tools.<br/>A few are rebuilding around AI.
        </h2>
        <p style="font-size:1rem;color:#8FAF8F;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:0.75rem;">The difference isn't budget. It's architecture. AI-native GTM isn't about which tools you have — it's about whether your entire revenue system is designed around AI from the start.</p>
        <p style="font-size:1rem;color:#00C853;font-weight:500;">The gap between them widens every quarter.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="flex:1.4;min-width:260px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1rem;">
        <div class="card-dark">
          <div style="font-family:'Instrument Serif',serif;font-size:2rem;font-style:italic;color:rgba(0,200,83,0.2);margin-bottom:0.75rem;">01</div>
          <div style="font-size:0.92rem;font-weight:600;color:#F0FFF0;margin-bottom:0.6rem;">The Tool Trap</div>
          <p style="font-size:0.84rem;color:#8FAF8F;line-height:1.7;">Buying Clay, Gong, and Apollo doesn't make you AI-native. Siloed tools without a connected architecture produce activity, not revenue.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-dark">
          <div style="font-family:'Instrument Serif',serif;font-size:2rem;font-style:italic;color:rgba(0,200,83,0.2);margin-bottom:0.75rem;">02</div>
          <div style="font-size:0.92rem;font-weight:600;color:#F0FFF0;margin-bottom:0.6rem;">The Strategy Gap</div>
          <p style="font-size:0.84rem;color:#8FAF8F;line-height:1.7;">AI amplifies what's already working. If your ICP, messaging, or pipeline motion is broken, AI makes it fail faster and at greater scale.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-dark">
          <div style="font-family:'Instrument Serif',serif;font-size:2rem;font-style:italic;color:rgba(0,200,83,0.2);margin-bottom:0.75rem;">03</div>
          <div style="font-size:0.92rem;font-weight:600;color:#F0FFF0;margin-bottom:0.6rem;">The Window</div>
          <p style="font-size:0.84rem;color:#8FAF8F;line-height:1.7;">The gap between AI-native and AI-decorated companies compounds every quarter. The window to lead this transformation is open — but it closes.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- WHAT GETS BUILT -->
<div class="rule"></div>
<section style="padding:5rem 2.5rem;background:#050D05;">
  <div style="max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;">
    <span class="lbl">The Architecture</span>
    <div class="mob-col" style="display:flex;gap:3rem;align-items:flex-start;margin-bottom:3rem;">
      <h2 style="font-family:'Instrument Serif',serif;font-size:clamp(1.8rem,3.5vw,2.6rem);font-weight:400;color:#F0FFF0;line-height:1.2;flex:1;min-width:240px;">What Gets Built<br/>In 90 Days</h2>
      <p style="font-size:0.95rem;color:#8FAF8F;line-height:1.8;flex:1.2;min-width:240px;padding-top:0.5rem;">AI-native GTM isn't a new tool layer — it's a rebuilt system. Here's what a complete AI-native revenue architecture actually contains.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="mob-col" style="display:flex;gap:1.25rem;flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <div class="card-mid">
        <div style="font-family:'Instrument Serif',serif;font-size:2.2rem;font-style:italic;color:#00C853;line-height:1;margin-bottom:1rem;">01</div>
        <div style="font-size:0.92rem;font-weight:600;color:#F0FFF0;margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Dynamic ICP System</div>
        <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:rgba(240,255,240,0.6);line-height:1.75;">A living ICP model that refines itself from win/loss data, intent signals, and conversion patterns — not a static document that goes stale in 90 days.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card-mid">
        <div style="font-family:'Instrument Serif',serif;font-size:2.2rem;font-style:italic;color:#00C853;line-height:1;margin-bottom:1rem;">02</div>
        <div style="font-size:0.92rem;font-weight:600;color:#F0FFF0;margin-bottom:0.75rem;">AI-Augmented Outbound</div>
        <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:rgba(240,255,240,0.6);line-height:1.75;">Outbound rebuilt around AI enrichment, true personalization at scale, and signal-based sequencing. Your team touches accounts the system has already pre-qualified.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card-mid">
        <div style="font-family:'Instrument Serif',serif;font-size:2.2rem;font-style:italic;color:#00C853;line-height:1;margin-bottom:1rem;">03</div>
        <div style="font-size:0.92rem;font-weight:600;color:#F0FFF0;margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Pipeline Intelligence</div>
        <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:rgba(240,255,240,0.6);line-height:1.75;">Dashboards and attribution that connect every GTM activity to revenue outcomes. So you can tell your board exactly what your AI investment is producing.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card-mid">
        <div style="font-family:'Instrument Serif',serif;font-size:2.2rem;font-style:italic;color:#00C853;line-height:1;margin-bottom:1rem;">04</div>
        <div style="font-size:0.92rem;font-weight:600;color:#F0FFF0;margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Revenue Workflows</div>
        <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:rgba(240,255,240,0.6);line-height:1.75;">Automations, handoffs, and AI-powered workflows that let a leaner team produce 3–4x the qualified pipeline without adding headcount proportionally.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
<div class="rule"></div>
<section id="process" style="padding:5rem 2.5rem;background:#0A1A0A;">
  <div style="max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;">
    <span class="lbl">The Process</span>
    <div class="mob-col" style="display:flex;gap:4rem;align-items:flex-start;">
      <div style="flex:1;min-width:240px;">
        <h2 style="font-family:'Instrument Serif',serif;font-size:clamp(1.8rem,3.5vw,2.6rem);font-weight:400;color:#F0FFF0;line-height:1.2;margin-bottom:1rem;">From First Call<br/>to Revenue Transformation</h2>
        <p style="font-size:0.9rem;color:#8FAF8F;line-height:1.8;">Most engagements reach full operational velocity within 90 days.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="flex:1.6;min-width:280px;">
        <div class="step-row">
          <div class="step-bar"></div>
          <div style="font-family:'Instrument Serif',serif;font-size:1.6rem;font-style:italic;color:#00C853;min-width:32px;line-height:1;">01</div>
          <div style="flex:1;">
            <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0.5rem;gap:0.5rem;flex-wrap:wrap;">
              <span style="font-size:0.95rem;font-weight:600;color:#F0FFF0;">Diagnose</span>
              <span style="font-size:0.68rem;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#4A6A4A;">Week 1–2</span>
            </div>
            <p style="font-size:0.84rem;color:#8FAF8F;line-height:1.75;">We audit your current GTM motion — ICP definition, outbound performance, pipeline mechanics, AI tool ROI — and identify exactly where the transformation opportunity lives.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="step-row">
          <div class="step-bar"></div>
          <div style="font-family:'Instrument Serif',serif;font-size:1.6rem;font-style:italic;color:#00C853;min-width:32px;line-height:1;">02</div>
          <div style="flex:1;">
            <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0.5rem;gap:0.5rem;flex-wrap:wrap;">
              <span style="font-size:0.95rem;font-weight:600;color:#F0FFF0;">Design & Build</span>
              <span style="font-size:0.68rem;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#4A6A4A;">Week 3–6</span>
            </div>
            <p style="font-size:0.84rem;color:#8FAF8F;line-height:1.75;">We design and implement the AI-native GTM architecture: dynamic ICP, AI-augmented outbound, pipeline intelligence, and the connected workflows that tie them together.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="step-row">
          <div class="step-bar"></div>
          <div style="font-family:'Instrument Serif',serif;font-size:1.6rem;font-style:italic;color:#00C853;min-width:32px;line-height:1;">03</div>
          <div style="flex:1;">
            <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0.5rem;gap:0.5rem;flex-wrap:wrap;">
              <span style="font-size:0.95rem;font-weight:600;color:#F0FFF0;">Lead</span>
              <span style="font-size:0.68rem;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#4A6A4A;">Week 7–10</span>
            </div>
            <p style="font-size:0.84rem;color:#8FAF8F;line-height:1.75;">You own the narrative internally. We give you the frameworks, the language, and the metrics to report to your board with confidence. The transformation is yours.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="step-row">
          <div class="step-bar"></div>
          <div style="font-family:'Instrument Serif',serif;font-size:1.6rem;font-style:italic;color:#00C853;min-width:32px;line-height:1;">04</div>
          <div style="flex:1;">
            <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0.5rem;gap:0.5rem;flex-wrap:wrap;">
              <span style="font-size:0.95rem;font-weight:600;color:#F0FFF0;">Transfer</span>
              <span style="font-size:0.68rem;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#4A6A4A;">Week 11–12</span>
            </div>
            <p style="font-size:0.84rem;color:#8FAF8F;line-height:1.75;">We hand off a system that runs without us. Your team owns it. We document everything. You leave with a working AI-native revenue motion and the playbook to scale it.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- WHO IT'S FOR -->
<div class="rule"></div>
<section id="who" style="padding:5rem 2.5rem;background:#050D05;">
  <div style="max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;">
    <span class="lbl">Who It's For</span>
    <h2 style="font-family:'Instrument Serif',serif;font-size:clamp(1.8rem,3.5vw,2.6rem);font-weight:400;color:#F0FFF0;line-height:1.2;max-width:600px;margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Built for Executives<br/>Who've Heard the Story</h2>
    <p style="font-size:0.92rem;color:#8FAF8F;margin-bottom:2.5rem;">If any of these sound familiar, we should talk.</p>
    <div class="mob-col" style="display:flex;gap:1.25rem;margin-bottom:2.5rem;">
      <div class="who-card">
        <div style="font-family:'Instrument Serif',serif;font-size:4rem;color:rgba(0,200,83,0.15);line-height:1;margin-bottom:0.75rem;">"</div>
        <p style="font-size:0.9rem;color:#F0FFF0;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:1.25rem;">A peer told me they cut their GTM team by 40% while growing pipeline. I want to understand if we can replicate that in our organization.</p>
        <p style="font-size:0.75rem;color:#4A6A4A;font-weight:500;">— CMO, $15M B2B SaaS</p>
      </div>
      <div class="who-card">
        <div style="font-family:'Instrument Serif',serif;font-size:4rem;color:rgba(0,200,83,0.15);line-height:1;margin-bottom:0.75rem;">"</div>
        <p style="font-size:0.9rem;color:#F0FFF0;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:1.25rem;">We've bought every AI tool on the market. My board is asking what the ROI is and I can't give them a clean answer.</p>
        <p style="font-size:0.75rem;color:#4A6A4A;font-weight:500;">— CRO, Series B Platform</p>
      </div>
      <div class="who-card">
        <div style="font-family:'Instrument Serif',serif;font-size:4rem;color:rgba(0,200,83,0.15);line-height:1;margin-bottom:0.75rem;">"</div>
        <p style="font-size:0.9rem;color:#F0FFF0;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:1.25rem;">I want to be the executive who led our AI transformation, not the one who's still explaining why we haven't started.</p>
        <p style="font-size:0.75rem;color:#4A6A4A;font-weight:500;">— CEO, Vertical SaaS</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div style="border-left:3px solid rgba(0,200,83,0.3);padding-left:1.5rem;max-width:600px;">
      <p style="font-size:0.72rem;font-weight:600;color:#4A6A4A;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Not the right fit</p>
      <p style="font-size:0.88rem;color:#8FAF8F;line-height:1.75;">This engagement is not for companies still finding product-market fit, or organizations looking to pilot a single AI tool. AI-native GTM transformation requires a working revenue motion to rebuild around.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- GAP ASSESSMENT -->
<div class="rule"></div>
<section style="padding:4rem 2.5rem;background:#0A1A0A;">
  <div style="max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;">
    <div class="quiz-box">
      <div class="badge"><span class="badge-dot"></span>3-Minute Assessment · Free</div>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Instrument Serif',serif;font-size:clamp(1.6rem,3vw,2.2rem);font-weight:400;color:#F0FFF0;line-height:1.2;max-width:560px;">Not sure where your AI-GTM gaps are?</h2>
      <p style="font-size:0.9rem;color:#8FAF8F;line-height:1.75;max-width:520px;">8 questions across the 4 pillars of AI-native GTM. A personalized gap report — with your score, pillar breakdown, and top 3 priority actions — delivered to your inbox in minutes.</p>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:1.25rem;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:center;">
        <a href="/quiz" class="btn-p">Take the Gap Assessment →</a>
        <span style="font-size:0.75rem;color:#4A6A4A;">No account required · Results in your inbox</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CREDIBILITY -->
<div class="rule"></div>
<section id="about" style="padding:5rem 2.5rem;background:#050D05;">
  <div style="max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;">
    <span class="lbl">The Operator</span>
    <div class="mob-col" style="display:flex;gap:4rem;align-items:flex-start;">
      <div style="flex:1;min-width:240px;">
        <h2 style="font-family:'Instrument Serif',serif;font-size:clamp(1.8rem,3.5vw,2.6rem);font-weight:400;color:#F0FFF0;line-height:1.2;margin-bottom:1rem;">Built by Someone<br/>Who's Done It Before</h2>
        <p style="font-size:0.92rem;color:#8FAF8F;line-height:1.8;">Not a consultant who theorizes about AI. Bill Colbert has built and rebuilt revenue motions at companies from pre-revenue to acquisition — including AI-native GTM implementations across B2B SaaS, consumer brands, and global enterprises.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="flex:1.4;min-width:260px;background:#0A1A0A;border:1px solid #1A3A1A;padding:2rem;">
        <div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:2rem;">
          <div style="flex:1;min-width:120px;padding:1rem;border-right:1px solid #1A3A1A;border-bottom:1px solid #1A3A1A;">
            <div style="font-family:'Instrument Serif',serif;font-size:2rem;font-style:italic;color:#00C853;line-height:1;margin-bottom:0.25rem;">$127M+</div>
            <div style="font-size:0.75rem;color:#8FAF8F;line-height:1.4;">Pipeline Generated</div>
          </div>
          <div style="flex:1;min-width:120px;padding:1rem;border-bottom:1px solid #1A3A1A;">
            <div style="font-family:'Instrument Serif',serif;font-size:2rem;font-style:italic;color:#F0FFF0;line-height:1;margin-bottom:0.25rem;">38</div>
            <div style="font-size:0.75rem;color:#8FAF8F;line-height:1.4;">GTM Systems Built</div>
          </div>
          <div style="flex:1;min-width:120px;padding:1rem;border-right:1px solid #1A3A1A;">
            <div style="font-family:'Instrument Serif',serif;font-size:2rem;font-style:italic;color:#F0FFF0;line-height:1;margin-bottom:0.25rem;">4.2x</div>
            <div style="font-size:0.75rem;color:#8FAF8F;line-height:1.4;">Avg Revenue Multiple</div>
          </div>
          <div style="flex:1;min-width:120px;padding:1rem;">
            <div style="font-family:'Instrument Serif',serif;font-size:2rem;font-style:italic;color:#00C853;line-height:1;margin-bottom:0.25rem;">90</div>
            <div style="font-size:0.75rem;color:#8FAF8F;line-height:1.4;">Days to Velocity</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <blockquote style="border-left:3px solid rgba(0,200,83,0.3);padding-left:1.25rem;">
